content.title: Congratulations
content.body:
You’ve successfully:

  • Generated the Edit Recipients screen
  • Created and customized the UI for the edit recipients screen
  • Update the services with the data
  • Added navigation to and from the edit Recipients screen
  • Added logout to the edit recipients screen

For more information on how to publish and share your app, check out the next hike: 9. Publish and Share the App.
